<body>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10539" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW">Select Address Block</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1053D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select, edit, or delete an address block layout for <link href="text/swriter/01/mailmerge03.xhp">mail merge</link>.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1054E" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Select the address block which you want to use</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10552" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select the block in the list box and click OK to use that block for mail merge addresses.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10555" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Never include the country/region</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10559" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select to never include a line with the country or region in the address block.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1055C" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Always include the country/region</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10560" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select to always include a line with the country or region in the address block.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10563" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Only include the country/region if different than:</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10567" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select to include a line with the country or region in the address block only if the value differs from the value you enter in the text box.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1056A" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">New</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1056E" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the <link href="text/swriter/01/mm_newaddblo.xhp">New Address Block</link> dialog, where you can define a new address block layout.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1057F" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Edit</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10583" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the <link href="text/swriter/01/mm_newaddblo.xhp">New Address Block</link> dialog, where you can edit the selected address block layout.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10594" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Delete</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10598" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Deletes the selected address block layout.</paragraph>
</body>
